.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, martial-arts, satire, musical
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person watching musical movies and the person watching satire movies##2
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
3. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching satire movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | martial-arts | musical | zombie |

