.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, collecting, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | cooking | drawing | collecting | hiking |

