2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person driving the trike is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |  3   |   4    |
| Transport   | tram | motorbike | trike | skateboard |

