.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-15::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, mouse, dog, rabbit
1. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the cat##2
3. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |    2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | rabbit | mouse | cat | dog |

