1. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |  2  |     3      |  4   |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | lizard | horse | hedgehog |

 